\& \- 633766 virt\-resize \-\-shrink fails
\& \- 633357 Updates to Spanish translation
\& \- 633096 virt\-resize calculates block device size incorrectly, doesn\*(Aqt work with qcow2 target
\& \- 629593 Dutch translation added
